{"tid":1432001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（理性分析）警察請入，你地真係就快輸！","createTime":"2019-08-08T06:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T16:36:28.000Z","uid":2719,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5ed868ab7207060a2bc6c6cb653806c829b2a20c","tid":1432001,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:26:24.000Z","msg":"拿～平時我都叫你地黑警/狗/死全家。<br />\n<br />\n但係呢個post，<br />\n我想平心靜氣同你地分析下個局勢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府唔撐你了！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由最初柒婆、高官、中聯辦、國務院都撐你地，<br />\n什麼對你地嘅肯定、合情合理。<br />\n到今日，開始拎獨立調查委員會岀黎談判。<br />\n你們應該要意識到，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">警隊會係第一個被犧牲</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n話我完全無分化就假嘅，但都睇下我講得有無道理。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">依家：<br />\n<br />\n- 微博網民開始屌香港警察<br />\n- 中聯辦話停止暴力後，考慮成立委員會<br />\n- 柒婆割蓆警隊，叫你地日日自己開show解話</span></span><br />\n<br />\n即係，港共、中共同支那人都已經唔撐你地。<br />\n撐你地嘅，得返香港班無文化廢中廢老。<br />\n<br />\n如果你地繼續堅持與民為敵：<br />\n1. 禍及全家<br />\n2. 港共清算<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果調轉槍頭，都仲有生機，<br />\n贏面仲要好大。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為港共連最後防線都反了。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以，我真係好希望你地諗清楚，<br />\n想唔想休息陪下老婆仔女、拍拖、打機，<br />\n定係仲想日日30幾度full gear係街曝曬。<br />\n<br />\n請冷靜諗我我講得岩唔岩，<br />\n如果你係認同嘅，麻煩些牙俾你地啲同事睇。<br />\n<br />\nThanks."},{"pid":"dc0a77becd86d0c946d4e9379e4d55259f3f3955","tid":1432001,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BhfcWrc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBhfcWrc.jpg&h=7439665c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1vuX7xS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1vuX7xS.jpg&h=1d1f746f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AOi